[[Exalted Mastery Vendor]]s are [[merchant]]s who will only offer trade after learning the [[Exalted Acceptance]] Mastery.

== Locations ==
;[[Heart of Maguuma]]
* [[Verdant Brink]] <small>(only during the [[Securing Verdant Brink]] [[map meta event]])</small>
** [[Noble Ledges]]—Next to {{waypoint|Faren's Flyer Waypoint}}
* [[Auric Basin]] <small>(cannot be accessed during the [[Battle in Tarir]] map meta event)</small>
** [[Tarir, the Forgotten City]]—Next to {{waypoint|Forgotten City Waypoint}}

