=== Merchant ===
{{Inventory|standard merchant}}

== Dialogue ==
;Without {{skill icon|Exalted Acceptance}} mastery trained
:My wares are quite special; I can only trade with someone I trust.
:{{dialogue icon|sell}} ''I can browse, but I don't think he'll sell me anything.''

;With Exalted Acceptance mastery trained
:Greetings. A celebrated hero such as yourself may need of what I have for sale.
:{{dialogue icon|sell}} ''Please show me your wares.''
:{{dialogue icon|end}} ''Not right now.''

== Notes ==
* Purchasing all 16 [[Auric weapons]] recipes costs 5,800 [[File: Lump of Aurillium.png|20px]] and purchasing one of each weapon shielding costs 4,000 [[File: Lump of Aurillium.png|20px]], for a total of 9,800.

