| type = chest
| req = Exalted Key
| requires = hot
}}
[[Exalted Chest]]s are a reward for completing the [[Battle in Tarir]] [[meta event]] in [[Auric Basin]]. Eight of these chests are located throughout a previously closed section of the tunnels beneath [[Tarir, the Forgotten City]]. Access to them is open for several minutes following the event's completion, before the section closes and [[player]]s are teleported out. Additional chests spawn at each outpost and pylon after each event chain is complete.

== Locations ==
;[[Heart of Maguuma]]
* [[Auric Basin]]
** [[Tarir, the Forgotten City]]

== Contents ==
* {{gather|Piece of Unidentified Gear}} or better.

* One of the following:
** {{gather|Pile of Bloodstone Dust|qty=2-3}}
** {{gather|Empyreal Fragment|qty=2-3}}
** {{gather|Milling Stone|qty=2-4}}

* Chance of {{gather|Lump of Aurillium|qty=5, 10 x 3|notes=[[Auric Basin]] only}} (Auric Basin only; none from home instance node)

* One of the following:
** {{gather|Agate Orb}}
** {{gather|Auric Ingot}}
** {{gather|Auric Sliver}}
** {{gather|Black Diamond}}
** {{gather|Ebony Orb}}
** {{gather|Leaf Fossil|qty=1-2}}
** {{gather|Maguuma Burl}}
** {{gather|Moonstone Orb}}
** {{gather|Pile of Auric Dust}}
** {{gather|Spirit Shard}}

* Chance of {{gather|Pile of Auric Dust|qty=5, 10}}

* Chance at one of the following:
** {{gather|Fallen Adventurer's Backpack}}
** {{gather|Feather-Lined Pouch}}
** {{gather|Heirloom Seed Pod}}
** {{gather|Noxious Seed Pod}}
** {{gather|Noxious Seed Pouch}}

* Low chance at one of the following:
** {{gather|Yassith's Weapon Recipe Book}}
** {{gather|Yassith's Armor Recipe Book}}
** {{gather|Viper's Weapon Recipe Book}}
** {{gather|Viper's Armor Recipe Book}}
** {{gather|Viper's Jewelry Recipe Book}}

* Very low chance at one of the following:
** {{gather|Berserker's Ley Guard's Revolver}}
** {{gather|Berserker's Ley Guard's Protector}}
** {{gather|Endless Exalted Bastion Tonic (container)}}

== Related chests ==
* [[Great Exalted Chest]] (14 chests)
* [[Grand Exalted Chest]] (5 chests)

== Notes ==
* You can get a daily Exalted Chest for your [[home instance]] or the [[homestead]] with the [[Personal Exalted Chest Voucher]].
** This chest always contains at least one {{gather|Piece of Rare Unidentified Gear}}.
* There is a maximum number of chests you can open per day (estimated to be around 50).

[[de:Erhabenen-Truhe]]
[[es:Cofre exaltado]]
[[fr:Coffre exalté]]

{{Object infobox
