[[Grand Exalted Chest]]s are a reward for successfully completing the [[Battle in Tarir (meta event)|Battle in Tarir]] [[meta event]] in [[Auric Basin]]. 5 of these chests are located throughout a previously closed section of the tunnels beneath Tarir, but are only available if the meta-event is successfully completed by players. Access to them is open for several minutes following the event's completion, before the section closes and players are teleported out.

== Location ==
;[[Heart of Maguuma]]
* [[Auric Basin]]
** [[Tarir, the Forgotten City]]

== Contents ==
* {{item icon|Piece of Rare Unidentified Gear}} or {{rarity|exotic}} gear.
* {{item icon|Piece of Unidentified Gear}} or better.
* {{item icon|Piece of Common Unidentified Gear}} or better.
* {{gather|Auric Sliver|chance=Guaranteed}}
* {{gather|Milling Stone|qty=1, 25|chance=Guaranteed}}

* One of the following:
** {{gather|Piles of Bloodstone Dust|qty=1-3}}
** {{gather|Empyreal Fragments|qty=1-3}}

* Chance of {{gather|Lump of Aurillium|qty=5 or 10 x 3}}

* One of the following:
** {{gather|Fallen Adventurer's Backpack}}
** {{gather|Feather-Lined Pouch}}
** {{gather|Heirloom Seed Pod}}
** {{gather|Noxious Seed Pod}}
** {{gather|Noxious Seed Pouch}}
** {{gather|Endless Exalted Bastion Tonic (container)}} (low chance instead of a bag)

* 1-2 of the following:
** {{gather|Agate Orb|qty=1-2}}
** {{gather|Auric Ingot|qty=1-2}}
** {{gather|Auric Sliver|qty=1-2}}
** {{gather|Black Diamond|qty=1-2}}
** {{gather|Ebony Orb|qty=1-2}}
** {{gather|Leaf Fossil|qty=1-2}}
** {{gather|Maguuma Burl|qty=1-2}}
** {{gather|Moonstone Orb|qty=1-2}}
** {{gather|Pile of Auric Dust|qty=1-2}}

* Low chance at one of the following:
** {{gather|Yassith's Weapon Recipe Book}}
** {{gather|Yassith's Armor Recipe Book}}
** {{gather|Viper's Weapon Recipe Book}}
** {{gather|Viper's Armor Recipe Book}}
** {{gather|Viper's Jewelry Recipe Book}}
** {{gather|Luminate's Keepsake}}

* Very rarely:
** {{gather|Augury of Death (weapon)}}
** {{gather|Berserker's Ley Guard's Revolver}}
** {{gather|Berserker's Ley Guard's Protector}}
** {{gather|Vial of Liquid Aurillium}}
** {{gather|Great Capra}}
** {{gather|Vision Crystal}}
** An [[ascended]] weapon box
** An [[ascended]] armor box

== Notes ==
* The 5 Grand chests, as well as 4 Great chests in the final room, are only available in case all four [[Octovine]]s have been defeated and the meta event was completed successfully.
** The Grand chests can be opened once a day without participating in the [[Battle in Tarir]] [[map meta event]] by joining after the event was successfully done. For additional openings of the chests in one day, a participation in the event is required.

== Trivia ==
* Prior to the [[Game updates/2021-12-14|December 14, 2021]] game update the [[Vial of Liquid Aurillium]] infusion was not directly contained within these chests, but was a part of the [[Charged Quartz Orichalcum Amulet of the Exalted]] which does drop from these chests.

== See also ==
* [[Exalted Chest]] (8 chests)
* [[Great Exalted Chest]] (14 chests)

